The netCDF operators NCO version 2.9.4 are ready. 

http://nco.sf.net (Homepage)
http://dust.ess.uci.edu/nco (Homepage "mirror")

This release fixes a bug where ncecat would segfaul when trying to
concatenate files with only scalar variables.

Enjoy,
Charlie

Feature changes:
1. None

Bug-fixes:
1. ncecat concatenates files without dimensions (all scalar variables)

Build changes:
1. Added ncecat, ncbo, ncea, ncflint tests to nco_tst.pl
2. Support AIX GCC builds in bld/Makefile

Other user-visible changes:
1. -r reports correct version again, and with cleaner formatting

User-invisible changes:
1. Change cvs.nco.sourceforge.net to cvs.sf.net in accord
   with new SourceForge BIND 9-induced policy
